I have an idea for an quick and wholesome thing you can do for Marine Senchou Gura. Create a treasure hunt in Minecraft for her to follow once she is back. Leave a sign on her ship in the JP server with instructions to somewhere in the EN server, and leave a sign there with directions to another sign. And at the end of the trail, maybe at your temple, leave a buried treasure chest under an X with some treasure and a message to her. 
I think you'd have fun doing that, and the payoff would be very cute right? It would work as a psuedo tour of the server as well, since the treasure hunt could lead her around to a few spots while looking for the sign!
If you do, just have the clues be simple, since they are going to be made harder thanks to the language barrier.
